title: The Based Farm Gets Baby Chickens
description:
I bought baby chickens from a neighbor and more from tractor supply, I've got a flock of 19 right now (5 pullets and 14 straight run) as these chickens mature I'll be able to figure out which are female and male right away.  I intend to keep 1 or 2 roosters for breeding my own chicks and the rest of the roosters will be culled and become feed for other animals.
